Title: Add builtin host label "cmk/site"
Class: feature
Compatible: comp
Component: core
Date: 1631785285
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0i1

Every host now discovers a builtin host label
<tt>cmk/site:[sitename]</tt>.

This can be used in rule conditions to filter
for hosts on specific sites
